Commissioner McGiven.

721
00:48:53,863 --> 00:48:54,163
Yes.

722
00:48:54,663 --> 00:48:55,503
Commissioner Hunt.

723
00:48:56,384 --> 00:48:56,684
Yes.

724
00:48:57,164 --> 00:48:58,304
Commissioner Brzezinski.

725
00:48:58,824 --> 00:48:59,104
Yes.

726
00:48:59,685 --> 00:49:00,325
Chief Buckley.

727
00:49:00,425 --> 00:49:00,705
Yes.

728
00:49:01,125 --> 00:49:07,086
