Your comments, please.

824
00:57:56,418 --> 00:58:03,279
So we actually own the building where the Dunkin' Donuts is with edible arrangements and Harrows.

825
00:58:04,399 --> 00:58:10,300
And we've always used that side street parking as trying to put employees out there.

826
