856
01:00:50,173 --> 01:00:50,914
in that building?

857
01:00:51,254 --> 01:00:52,395
Like why three hours?

858
01:00:54,476 --> 01:00:58,899
Um, I mean, the physical therapy has people there for more than an hour.

859
01:00:58,919 --> 01:01:00,780
I'm not really sure.

860
01:01:00,860 --> 01:01:01,881
But okay.

861
01:01:02,101 --> 01:01:03,982
I mean, it's not really that necessary.

862
01:01:04,362 --> 01:01:10,426
I was just trying to see if if our employees did park there, you know, sometimes they have like a four hour shift, you know, they could park there.

863
01:01:10,967 --> 01:01:13,348
We're trying to keep people employees out of the lot.

864
01:01:13,448 --> 01:01:18,872
But if we have to buy a business pass, for all of our employees, you're talking

865
01:01:19,715 --> 01:01:20,275
a lot of money.

866
01:01:23,776 --> 01:01:24,396
Okay, thank you.

867
01:01:24,416 --> 01:01:30,017
Because there's a lot of businesses there, and if everyone parked their car in the lot, then there would be no place for our customers to park.

868
01:01:32,818 --> 01:01:33,558
Yep, correct.

869
01:01:34,158 --> 01:01:35,539
Okay, thank you very much.

870
01:01:35,619 --> 01:01:37,819
I do appreciate the comments.

871
01:01:38,039 --> 01:01:39,659
