898
01:03:44,383 --> 01:03:52,071
So clearly, and I don't want to finger anybody here, but we have to because people live in this neighborhood, right?

899
01:03:52,431 --> 01:03:56,175
And if you hear frustration in my voice, it's because I am frustrated.

900
01:03:56,576 --> 01:03:59,999
There's 25 to 30 cars from the auto body shop.

901
01:04:00,499 --> 01:04:04,163
Whoever owns the auto body shop is using this as an extension of their business.

902
01:04:04,183 --> 01:04:05,224
They're using the street

903
01:04:06,045 --> 01:04:12,052
