904
01:04:12,372 --> 01:04:14,194
That has to stop, right?

905
01:04:14,454 --> 01:04:16,456
There are people who live in this neighborhood.

906
01:04:16,817 --> 01:04:17,918
I have a three-year-old.

907
01:04:18,238 --> 01:04:20,901
